{"tid":545832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳日君撰文揭兩中國主教遭梵蒂岡「迫宮」 教廷罕有譴責","createTime":"2018-01-31T02:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T14:40:27.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"a7ab46ae2e9763d923e1d4dc7442b6969ff96a10","tid":545832,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T02:13:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180130/large/1517325589_5ae7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180130%2Flarge%2F1517325589_5ae7.png&h=022d379d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n教廷發言人於羅馬時間周二下午罕有發表聲明，不點名批評天主教香港教區榮休主教陳日君樞機的言論製造混亂和爭議。陳周一發表網誌，確認教內傳言，指梵蒂岡要求兩名中國主教辭職，讓位予中共承認的人選；他月初就此事親往梵蒂岡向教宗陳情，引述教宗指不會讓「迫宮」事件在中國發生，行文多次暗示教廷中人阻礙教宗得知中國教會真相。<br />\n<br />\n教廷發言人指，教宗與國務卿在中國事務上有恆常聯繫，了解中國教會的情況，對於教會中人提出相反言論感意外及遺憾。陳日君網誌現時未能連上，未知是否被關閉。消息人士指，相信與網站伺服器故障有關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180131/57774090\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180131%2F57774090&d=8Bx7RVfFyB9QLKvfWl4srDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=454f2c83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180131%2F57774090&h=adda54f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180131/57774090</a>"},{"pid":"219653e8ead81e0ddb4ac2b755dd724d42343be3","tid":545832,"uid":63909,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T02:14:33.000Z","msg":"天主教廷一直都係仆街黎架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8603c7628a1bf3563b720ab2cc4006f95271c0","tid":545832,"uid":38671,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T02:24:20.000Z","msg":"而家開始擔心陳日君安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb8a285a63e3f87b9e5850a138e8d7b27e8af39